snippet.title: [Solo Leveling:ARISE] Character Teaser #2: Choi Jong-In
snippet.description:
✨[Solo Leveling:ARISE]✨ 

See Choi Jong-In in action.

The guild master of the Hunters Guild and the best in South Korea.
He's been nicknamed "The Ultimate Hunter." This S-Rank Mage-type hunter
mainly uses his Fire Magic, and can burn down a building
quicker than the blink of an eye.

Want to learn more? Then keep a lookout for updates on our official channels: 

■ Official Website
https://sololeveling.netmarble.com

■ Official Twitter
https://twitter.com/Sololv_ARISE_GL

■ Official Facebook
https://www.facebook.com/SoloLevelingARISE.EN/
https://www.facebook.com/SoloLevelingARISE.TH/

■ Official Instagram
